Janmadin ki hardik badhai sita!

meri Priye, sakhi, anje, tejaswini, indumati, janu, anju, ganju, patni ji, anjali ji, meri radha, or meri pyari sita aapko aapke is janmdin avtaran din ki badhai ho. meri radha ye pahla birthday he meri sagai ke baad. mujhe intezar to bahut tha aaaj ke din ka. Aaj aap 22 saal ke pure ho gaye ho ab aap shadi ke layak ho gaye ho To shadi kar lo meto kahta hu. has kya rahe ho kar lo majak nhi kar raha. thik he. Aap is saal se LLB shuru kar rahe ho iske liye aapko badhai or aap isko man lagakar puri karoge esi meri aasha he. 